<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_150_r2l13"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hochvvir<ex>di</ex>k<ex>eit</ex></expan> nehſt aber <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_150_r2l14">von der hab vnd kauffmanſchaft wegen dıe den ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vor </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_150_r2l15"><expan>cʒeite<ex>n</ex></expan> in <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> Stat cʒu Prünne <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> iſt woꝛden / <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_150_r2l16">dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> vvol </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_150_line_1576581248514_4193">wol </ab></add> fürbraht / vvie ewr gnade 
<add><ab facs="#facs_150_line_1576581251279_4198">ſich </ab></add> darynne gen Jn gar </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_150_r2l17">gnedıklich bevveiſet hab / doch ſo ſeẏ Jn der ſache noch khein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_150_r2l18">ende vvoꝛden / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> fürſtenlich gnade noch darcʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_150_r2l19">vvenden vnd ſchicken vnd <expan>beſtelle<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet / daʒ den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_150_r2l20">dieſelb Jr habe gekert vnd <expan>v<ex>er</ex>golte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vverde<ex>n</ex></expan> / Als etc / das <expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_150" id="74v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Margraf Jobsen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als wir
                                                  <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hochwir<ex>di</ex>k<ex>eit</ex></expan> nehst
                                                aber <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von der hab und
                                                kauffmanschaft wegen, die den
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vor
                                                  <expan>czeite<ex>n</ex></expan> in
                                                  <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> stat czu Prünne
                                                  <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> ist worden,
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns die
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<add>wol</add> fürbraht, wie ewr gnade
                                                  <add>sich</add> darynne gen in gar gnediklich
                                                beweiset hab, doch so sey in der sache noch khein
                                                ende worden. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> fürstenlich gnade noch
                                                darczu wenden und schicken und
                                                  <expan>bestelle<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet, daz den
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dieselb ir habe
                                                gekert und
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>golte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan>. Als etc. Das
                                                  <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
